Backup Script Project

Overview

This project is a simple automated backup solution using `rsync`.

---

Features

* Incremental backups
* Excludes unnecessary files
* Logs backup activity
* Uses hard links to save space

---

Why This Matters

Backups are critical in system administration. This script demonstrates:

* Automation
* File synchronization
* Disaster recovery basics

---

Usage

```bash
chmod +x backup.sh
./backup.sh
```

